title: USAD 2006-2007 The Music Of China
description:
United States Academic Decathlon presents The Music of China CD from the official USAD curriculum from last year. It&#039;s a collection of songs from throughout China&#039;s musical history. To be honest it&#039;s actually pretty good.

Includes folk songs, instrumentals, old Chinese opera music, "Two Butterflies" (a modern cantopop song), and others.

It&#039;s in 320 kb/s mp3. Oh yeah and I added scans of the cover/ song list too.
